口神咒 丹朱口神，吐秽除氛。舌神正伦，通</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道</category><category>咒</category></item><item><title>金刚经摘要</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E4%BD%9B/%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E7%BB%8F-%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E4%BD%9B/%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E7%BB%8F-%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81/</guid><description>第一品 法会因由分 第二品 善现启请分 应云何住，云何降伏其心。 第三品 大乘正宗分 如是灭度无量无数无边众生, 实无众生得灭度者。 若菩萨有我相, 人相, 众生</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>金刚经</category><category>性功</category><category>摘要</category><category>佛</category></item><item><title>金花的秘密</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86/</guid><description>译者按：《太乙金华宗旨》共有十三章，卫礼贤只翻译了前八章，且有个别段落没有译出来，后面五章卫礼贤觉得价值没有那么大而未译出。《慧命经》全书共</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>金花的秘密</category><category>太乙金华宗旨</category><category>吕洞宾</category><category>纯阳真人</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>青华秘文</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87/</guid><description>玉清金笥青华秘文金宝内炼丹诀 紫阳真人张伯端撰 远师真人王邦叔授 东和希古渔人刘元一受 序 远师真人王邦叔，不知何许人也。时年十九，侍紫阳真人为弟子。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>青华秘文</category><category>张伯端</category><category>紫阳真人</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>南宗</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>高上玉皇心印妙经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上药三品，神与气精，恍恍惚惚，杳杳冥冥. 存无守有，顷刻而成，回风混合，百日功灵。 默朝上帝，一纪飞升，智者易悟，昧者难行。 履践天光，呼吸育清，</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄帝阴符经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上篇 观天之道，执天之行，尽矣。故天有五贼，见之者昌。五贼在心，施行于天。宇宙在乎手，万化生乎身。天性，人也；人心，机也。立天之道，以定人也。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>阴符经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>性功</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭中景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>念吾头顶戴天神 发为星辰万余纶 纡长槃屈光若玄 顶上中央名通天 孔德之容大如钱 天星和气从此间 养人骨髓浸灵根 下和六府绍五宫 消除恶气出脐门 还念两目白黑分</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄庭经</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭内景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%86%85%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%86%85%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid>